his along with mic drop next turn.\" Subsequently, JustSomeDude considered playing 'Deadly Poison' and ended his turn. The opponent's turn began with the play of 'Raging Felscreamer', which announced, \"I hunger!\" and reduced the cost of the next Demon. Survivor Xyrella then used her Hero Power, Demon Claws, to gain +1 Attack, striking JustSomeDude's hero, Valeera Sanguinar, and reducing her health from 22 to 19. On his turn, JustSomeDude played 'Bloodsail Raider', followed by 'Silver Serpent', which declared \"Unleash now!\" as it appeared with Rush, Poisonous, and Immune this turn. He also played 'Magtheridon, Unreleased', a 1-cost Mech Demon entering a Dormant state. JustSomeDude strategized, stating, \"All right, definitely need to find some weapon durability here,\" and \"I think the snake is quite good,\" pondering the dormant minion, \"Am I playing a T-set? You're waking up, right?\" In a later phase, JustSomeDude played a 3-cost 'Silver Serpent', which attacked Mire's 4/4 minion, destroying it and reducing Survivor Xyrella's health to 19. Mire countered by playing a 6-cost 'Window Shopper', summoning a 6/5 Demon minion that declared, \"I am ready!\" followed by a 2-cost 'Saloon Brewmaster' and another 'Window Shopper', summoning a 3/3 Demon minion that stated, \"Don't tell I was made just for me.\" JustSomeDude remarked, \"Oh, well, that's annoying.\" The opponent's buffed 3/3 minion returned, proclaiming, \"Who's ready for another round?\" JustSomeDude observed, \"This is for sure Arena deck, right? The Raging Felscreamer kinda give it away, but for sure now,\" as minion attack sounds indicated damage to his hero, Valeera Sanguinar, whose health was now 19. On his turn, JustSomeDude played a 2-cost 'Harmonic Hip Hop', dealing 1 damage and giving his weapon +3 Attack, noting aloud, \"Plus three attack on my weapon.\" He then used a 1-cost 'Thistle Tea Set', drawing a card and further boosting his weapon. Presented with a 'Choose One' effect offering Aftersh